item.name: Find Tag Usage by Tag Link
Find IP Addresses by Subnet Range
Find Connected Resource by Network Interface
Find Subnet Range by Sub Network
Find IaaS IP Address by IP
Get IaaS Network Interfaces of vRA

body.raw:
{
    "projectId": "db1ffedd-6e4c-444a-9245-8b79abc330fb",
    "name": "SAMPLE - VM - BASIC - 2",
    "requestScopeOrg": true,
    "content": "formatVersion: 1
inputs:
  projectId:
    type: string
    title: Project ID
  zoneId:
    type: string
    title: Cloud
    $dynamicEnum: /data/vro-actions/com.vmk.action/getCloudZones?projectId={{projectId}}
  computeType:
    type: string
    title: Cloud Type
    $dynamicDefault: /data/vro-actions/com.vmk.action/getComputeType?zoneId={{zoneId}}
  computeTag:
    type: string
    title: Compute
    $dynamicEnum: /data/vro-actions/com.vmk.action/getComputeTags?zoneId={{zoneId}}
  networkTag:
    type: string
    title: Network
    $dynamicEnum: /data/vro-actions/com.vmk.action/getNetworkTags?zoneId={{zoneId}}
  address:
    type: string
    title: IP Address
    default: ''
    $dynamicEnum: /data/vro-actions/com.vmk.action/getAvailableIPAddressesByNetworkTag?zoneId={{zoneId}}&networkTag={{networkTag}}
  flavor:
    type: string
    title: Flavor
    $dynamicEnum: /data/vro-actions/com.vmk.action/getFlavors
  image:
    type: string
    title: Image
    $dynamicEnum: /data/vro-actions/com.vmk.action/getImages
resources:
  vm:
    type: Cloud.Machine
    metadata:
      layoutPosition:
        - 0
        - 0
    properties:
      image: ${input.image}
      flavor: ${input.flavor}
      networks:
        - network: ${resource.net.id}
          assignment: static
          address: ${input.address!=""?input.address:null}
      constraints:
        - tag: ${input.computeTag}
  net:
    type: Cloud.Network
    metadata:
      layoutPosition:
        - 1
        - 0
    properties:
      networkType: existing
      constraints:
        - tag: ${input.networkTag}
"
}
